{"tid":1244706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇透] 睇神探比卡超學到點辨認便衣, 有冇人討論下?","createTime":"2019-06-20T04:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T05:15:10.000Z","uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eacf0df0a9c9d94f4c6368ee04cd4b3576e6ec","tid":1244706,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"男主角老豆其實就係Deadpool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有人唔信佢係警察, 就會起疑心...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到疑似警察, 可以問(舉香港為例)<br />\n<br />\n1.你係咪警察<br />\n<br />\n2.你係咪便裝執勤, 請你出示委任證<br />\n<br />\n3.如果你拒絕出示,<br />\n我會保留影片用黎查詢及投訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周圍望, 單邊耳機, 企高地,<br />\n點煙唔食煙, 無目的地拍片<br />\n可以留意下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你望實佢佢會閃, 扮玩電話, 扮點煙<br />\n扮傾電話, 另轉身, 老套背囊, 少少鬆啲衫<br />\n狗成都係便衣<br />\n<br />\n如果佢話佢唔係執勤仲簡單,<br />\n同佢講你地環頭有簽到簿,<br />\n亦都有每日Daily Report<br />\n有晒上更下更同當更狗數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef :<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員在以下情況須出示警察委任證：<br />\n<br />\n便衣警務人員：在行使警察權力時，必須表明身分及出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n軍裝警務人員：一般無須主動出示警察委任證，但如市民提出要求，他們亦須出示委任證，除非情況不容許，或要求不合理。<br />\n<br />\n　　<br />\n當警務人員出示委任證，只須向提出要求的市民展示委任證，而不可將委任證轉交任何市民查閱。 如市民對警務人員身份或委任證存有懷疑，可立即聯絡就近警署 查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html#q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F13_faqs%2Ffaq_g.html%23q4&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbEv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=679892d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/13_faqs/faq_g.html#q4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似有啲離題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完之後終於明白晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n套戲我比60 分, 不值入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97552ef971f2332ff3c228b8d7001c0468dc3ecf","tid":1244706,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:49:00.000Z","msg":"確定係便衣就吹雞,用麻包袋,之後唔洗我教啦"},{"pid":"a97d4f073679b8839e11a437cbde299a495ed4c3","tid":1244706,"uid":119916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"直接問 師兄，而家情況點"},{"pid":"f40c99c51545d6e5a2fe9143624b83d7357adc55","tid":1244706,"uid":48011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"問下傻強咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}